724853f-a.title: Manhattan: York Avenue - 62nd Street (East).
724853f-a.text:
York Avenue, west side, south from East 62nd
Street, showing gas holders at this point. To
the left is the Oueensboro Bridge paralleling
59th Street and from which point south,York Avenue
alters its identity to Sutton Place.
